# Cross-origin isolation for the whole site so SharedArrayBuffer is available (the Python IDE's
# Web Worker uses it for BLOCKING input() via Atomics.wait). COEP `credentialless` is the permissive
# variant: cross-origin no-cors subresources (Pyodide from jsDelivr, ffmpeg-core from unpkg) load
# without each needing a CORP header — they are fetched without credentials. COOP `same-origin`
# completes the isolation. Applied by Cloudflare Workers Assets directly (no Worker round-trip).
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
